# SecIdentity

**Class**

An abstract Core Foundation-type object representing an identity.

## Declaration

```swift
class SecIdentity
```

## Overview

A [doc://com.apple.security/documentation/Security/SecIdentity] object contains a [doc://com.apple.security/documentation/Security/SecKey] object and an associated [doc://com.apple.security/documentation/Security/SecCertificate] object.
